        <h2>Benefits of Juicing</h2>
        <div class="benefit">
            <p><strong>Boosts Immunity:</strong> Fresh juices are packed with vitamins and minerals that strengthen your immune system.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="benefit">
            <p><strong>Improves Digestion:</strong> Juices are easy on the digestive system, allowing your body to absorb nutrients more efficiently.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="benefit">
            <p><strong>Enhances Energy:</strong> The natural sugars in fruits and vegetables provide a quick and healthy energy boost.</p>
