        <h2>Juice Recipes</h2>
        <div class="recipe">
            <h3>Green Detox Juice</h3>
            <p><strong>Ingredients:</strong> 1 cucumber, 2 celery stalks, 1 green apple, 1 handful of spinach, juice of 1 lemon.</p>
            <p><strong>Instructions:</strong> Blend all ingredients together until smooth. Serve chilled.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="recipe">
            <h3>Carrot-Orange Delight</h3>
            <p><strong>Ingredients:</strong> 4 carrots, 2 oranges, 1-inch piece of ginger.</p>
            <p><strong>Instructions:</strong> Juice the carrots and oranges. Add ginger and mix well. Serve fresh.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="recipe">
            <h3>Berry Blast Juice</h3>
            <p><strong>Ingredients:</strong> 1 cup of mixed berries (strawberries, blueberries, raspberries), 1 apple, 1/2 cup of water.</p>
            <p><strong>Instructions:</strong> Blend all ingredients until smooth. Add more water if needed. Enjoy!</p>
        </div>
    </div>

